{"tid":640611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞又斬人（元朗）","createTime":"2018-04-24T11:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T13:05:56.000Z","uid":43678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a21046b37a0fb972305fe88693b52c1c25a7c538","tid":640611,"uid":43678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"南亞兇徒肆虐元朗！消息稱，下午6時許，一名年約20歲男子在教育路一麵店食麵時，突有4至5名南亞口罩惡煞持刀闖至施襲，他遭狂斬，立即逃至附近後巷躲避，惟遭兇徒趕上再次揮刀襲擊，兇徒逞兇後乘座接應私家車離開。 <br />\n<br />\n有人見狀報警，救護員接報趕抵，其時事主已陷入昏迷，送院搶救。警方正在現場調查事件，案件交新界北總區反三合會行動組跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，事主疑有黑幫背景，他前臂、腳等多處中10多刀受傷。警方事後在約5公里外的屯門亦園路一天橋底，發現一部被燒毀私家車，懷疑與案有關，初步相信兇徒燒車毀證<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180424/mobile/bkn-20180424184321578-0424_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180424%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180424184321578-0424_00822_001.html&d=pUcAvh2t%2F5dmdOO84wTasMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=85e247b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180424/mobile/bkn-20180424184321578-0424_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/194248_0462bad15f813f454a05df243b774b9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F194248_0462bad15f813f454a05df243b774b9a.png&h=372338db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b95f7967d70ea2894b6a3f7697e900ddcfdf45a6","tid":640611,"uid":85819,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ad5fbcc55c13a383632628b8d15da6ab459072d","tid":640611,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91d55c671dd5b4b3735c895c0a463b96d9fb4d15","tid":640611,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:51:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f63b43ff1dd8faa8880be1a2737afe78cb229d2","tid":640611,"uid":143499,"like":7,"disli